is.prime  <-  function ( number )  {   if ( number  <=  1 )  {   return ( FALSE )   }  else  if ( number  <=  3 )  {   return ( TRUE )   }    if ( number  %%  2  ==  0  ||  number  %%  3  ==  0 )  {   return ( FALSE )   }    i  <-  5   while ( i * i  <=  number )  {   if ( number  %%  i  ==  0  ||  number  %%  ( i +2 )  ==  0 )  {   return ( FALSE )   }   i  =  i  +  6   }   return ( TRUE )  }  Dart  This test is in Dart using the same optimization as above.
